# Vincent — screens

Navigation lives in `App.kt`: bottom tabs (Home · Racks · Bottles · Search) + stack overlays.

## Main tabs

| Tab | File |
|-----|------|
| Dashboard | `DashboardScreen.kt` |
| Racks (Colour/Price/Vintage/Category) | `CellarScreen.kt` |
| Bottle list/grid | `BottlesScreen.kt` |
| Search & filters | `SearchScreen.kt` |

## Overlays (from `App.kt` `Dest`)

| Screen | File |
|--------|------|
| Bottle detail | `BottleDetailScreen.kt` |
| Add (scan/photo/voice/manual) | `AddScreen.kt` |
| Edit bottle | `BottleEditScreen.kt` |
| Login | `LoginScreen.kt` |
| Account | `AccountScreen.kt` |
| Settings | `SettingsScreen.kt` |
| Import/Export CSV | `DataManagementScreen.kt` |
| Recents | `RecentScreen.kt` |
| AR rack view | `ArScreen.kt` (+ `ArScreen.android.kt`) |
| Rack edit | `RackEditScreen.kt` |
| Tastings | `TastingsScreen.kt`, `TastingEditScreen.kt` |
| Management | `WinesManagementScreen.kt`, `RacksManagementScreen.kt`, `RegionsManagementScreen.kt`, `ProducersScreen.kt`, `SuppliersScreen.kt` |
| Debug logcat | `LogcatScreen.kt` |

## Patterns

- Screens read from `Cellar` (derived lists) and call narrow mutation APIs.
- Add flow: barcode → `ProductLookup` / photo → `WineRecognizer` / voice → `Dictation` + AI / manual form → confirm.
- Do not duplicate navigation logic — extend `Dest` in `App.kt`.
